559
00:38:26,985 --> 00:38:29,782
Be a man, Afzal Subhanallah.

560
00:38:29,782 --> 00:38:31,419
I find those who talk politics

561
00:38:31,419 --> 00:38:32,841
Before saying 'I love you'

562
00:38:32,841 --> 00:38:35,794
Rather toxic!

563
00:38:42,230 --> 00:38:44,597
