00:39:38,582 --> 00:39:39,213
Farah!

579
00:39:39,213 --> 00:39:41,983
Farah Ibrahim!

580
00:39:42,509 --> 00:39:43,436
There!

581
00:39:43,436 --> 00:39:47,760
